snippet.title: Pinori: TEXT ADVENTURE EDITION! (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Do you like text adventure games? Are you in need of another lightweight game? Perhaps another time killer? If you answered yes to any of those questions, PyNori is the perfect fit for you!

Download it for FREE at: https://shirley-xml.itch.io/pynori
Payment is OPTIONAL! Only pay for the game if you wish to donate to the developer.

Want notifications for devlogs and updates? Follow the game's Twitter account! https://x.com/pinoripython

#pynori #python #programming #textadventure #rpg #pinori #gameplay #games #game #gamer #gamers #pygame #trailer #trailers 
Other: PolyMars, Code Bullet, FaceDev, Ardens
